text: Kiya aap ney unhen nahi dekha? Jin ka daawa to yeh hai kay jo kuch aap per aur jo kuch aap say pehlay utara gaya hai uss per unn ka eman hai lekin woh apney faislay ghair ullah ki taraf ley jana chahtay hain halankay unhen hukum diya gaya hai kay shetan ka inkar keren shetan to yeh chahata hai unhen behka ker door daal dey
